The Shiny App
========================================================

This app explores Ratings of State Judges in the US Superior Court from USJudgeRatings dataset containing 43 observations on 12 numeric variables.

Variables
========================================================

Variables description:

- CONT  Number of contacts of lawyer with judge.
- INTG  Judicial integrity.
- DMNR	Demeanor.
- DILG	Diligence.
- CFMG	Case flow managing.
- DECI	Prompt decisions.
- PREP	Preparation for trial.
- FAMI	Familiarity with law.
- ORAL	Sound oral rulings.
- WRIT	Sound written rulings.
- PHYS	Physical ability.
- RTEN	Worthy of retention.
Layout
========================================================

The Layout is a Basic Table extracted from Shiny gallery applyed to USJudgeRatings Data Set.
Reference: http://shiny.rstudio.com/gallery/basic-datatable.html

Usage:
========================================================

Use the select lists and text boxes to filter main variables into the table.
